    <note>Li(2) Jifu [3480] See documentation for descendant, Zhounan [3487]. Jifu was Xianzong's zaixiang twice, once in 806 and again in 811. His #1 son, Dexiu [15160], was a Chizhou cishi, whereas his #2 son, Deyu [15161], was Wenzong's zaixiang. Renming Da cidian, p. 386; XTS, 72A.72a. JTS, 148.3992-97. XTS, 146.1a-3b. ZZTJ, 237.7626, 7635, 7639, 7655, 238.7682, 239.7705, 7707.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:806:  Apt. Hanlin xueshi806:  Apt. Zhongshu shilang, Tong pingzhang shi (Zaixiang)808:  Apt. HUainan jiedu shi811:  Spt. Zhongshu shilang, Tong pingzhang shi (Zaixiang).814:  Died in office as Zaixiang. 《唐代人物知識ベース》記其生卒年為：758 - 814.</note>
